{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "START",
      "type": "start",
      "text": "Good evening. Let’s take a moment to reflect on your day.",
      "next": "A1_Q1"
    },
    {
      "id": "A1_Q1",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "How would you describe your day overall?",
      "options": ["Productive", "Tough", "Mixed", "Frustrating"],
      "nextMap": {
        "Productive": "A1_Q2_POS",
        "Mixed": "A1_Q2_POS",
        "Tough": "A1_Q2_NEG",
        "Frustrating": "A1_Q2_NEG"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "A1_Q2_POS",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "When something went well today, what made it happen?",
      "options": [
        "I planned and executed it well",
        "The team supported me",
        "Things just worked out",
        "I adapted when needed"
      ],
      "signalMap": {
        "I planned and executed it well": "axis1:internal",
        "The team supported me": "axis1:internal",
        "Things just worked out": "axis1:external",
        "I adapted when needed": "axis1:internal"
      },
      "next": "A1_REFLECT"
    },
    {
      "id": "A1_Q2_NEG",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "When things didn’t go as planned, what was your first reaction?",
      "options": [
        "Tried to focus on what I could control",
        "Waited for things to change",
        "Felt stuck",
        "Pushed through anyway"
      ],
      "signalMap": {
        "Tried to focus on what I could control": "axis1:internal",
        "Waited for things to change": "axis1:external",
        "Felt stuck": "axis1:external",
        "Pushed through anyway": "axis1:internal"
      },
      "next": "A1_REFLECT"
    },
    {
      "id": "A1_REFLECT",
      "type": "decision",
      "conditions": [
        {
          "if": "axis1.internal >= axis1.external",
          "goto": "A1_REFLECT_INT"
        },
        {
          "if": "axis1.external > axis1.internal",
          "goto": "A1_REFLECT_EXT"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "A1_REFLECT_INT",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "You noticed your role in shaping what happened today. Even small decisions count — that’s where change begins.",
      "next": "A1_Q3"
    },
    {
      "id": "A1_REFLECT_EXT",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "It’s natural to feel pulled by circumstances. But even in tough moments, there’s usually a small space where you chose how to respond.",
      "next": "A1_Q3"
    },
    {
      "id": "A1_Q3",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "Looking back, where did you have the most control today?",
      "options": [
        "How I approached problems",
        "How I managed my time",
        "I didn’t feel much control",
        "How I responded emotionally"
      ],
      "signalMap": {
        "How I approached problems": "axis1:internal",
        "How I managed my time": "axis1:internal",
        "I didn’t feel much control": "axis1:external",
        "How I responded emotionally": "axis1:internal"
      },
      "next": "A1_FINAL"
    },
    {
      "id": "A1_FINAL",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "Today wasn’t just something that happened to you. You influenced parts of it — through actions, decisions, or responses.",
      "next": "BRIDGE_1_2"
    },
    {
      "id": "BRIDGE_1_2",
      "type": "bridge",
      "text": "Now let’s shift perspective — from what you controlled, to what you contributed.",
      "next": "A2_Q1"
    },
    {
      "id": "A2_Q1",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "Think about one interaction you had today. What stands out most?",
      "options": [
        "I helped someone with something",
        "I shared knowledge or guidance",
        "I needed support from others",
        "I felt others weren’t doing enough"
      ],
      "signalMap": {
        "I helped someone with something": "axis2:contribution",
        "I shared knowledge or guidance": "axis2:contribution",
        "I needed support from others": "axis2:contribution",
        "I felt others weren’t doing enough": "axis2:entitlement"
      },
      "next": "A2_Q2"
    },
    {
      "id": "A2_Q2",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "In that situation, how did you show up?",
      "options": [
        "I focused on solving the problem",
        "I made sure others were aligned",
        "I expected others to step up",
        "I felt I was doing more than my share"
      ],
      "signalMap": {
        "I focused on solving the problem": "axis2:contribution",
        "I made sure others were aligned": "axis2:contribution",
        "I expected others to step up": "axis2:entitlement",
        "I felt I was doing more than my share": "axis2:entitlement"
      },
      "next": "A2_DECIDE"
    },
    {
      "id": "A2_DECIDE",
      "type": "decision",
      "conditions": [
        {
          "if": "axis2.contribution >= axis2.entitlement",
          "goto": "A2_REFLECT_CONTRIB"
        },
        {
          "if": "axis2.entitlement > axis2.contribution",
          "goto": "A2_REFLECT_ENTITLE"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "A2_REFLECT_CONTRIB",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "You leaned toward contribution today — focusing on what you could add, not just what you received.",
      "next": "A2_Q3"
    },
    {
      "id": "A2_REFLECT_ENTITLE",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "It’s easy to notice gaps in others’ effort. But focusing only there can hide where you still had room to contribute.",
      "next": "A2_Q3"
    },
    {
      "id": "A2_Q3",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "Looking back, where could you have contributed just a little more?",
      "options": [
        "Offering help earlier",
        "Communicating more clearly",
        "Taking ownership of a gap",
        "I already gave my best"
      ],
      "signalMap": {
        "Offering help earlier": "axis2:contribution",
        "Communicating more clearly": "axis2:contribution",
        "Taking ownership of a gap": "axis2:contribution",
        "I already gave my best": "axis2:entitlement"
      },
      "next": "A2_FINAL"
    },
    {
      "id": "A2_FINAL",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "Contribution isn’t about doing everything. It’s about noticing where you can move things forward — even in small ways.",
      "next": "BRIDGE_2_3"
    },
    {
      "id": "BRIDGE_2_3",
      "type": "bridge",
      "text": "Now let’s widen the lens — beyond what you did, to who it impacted.",
      "next": "A3_Q1"
    },
    {
      "id": "A3_Q1",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "When you think about today’s biggest challenge, who comes to mind first?",
      "options": [
        "Just me — I was dealing with it myself",
        "My team — we were all involved",
        "A specific colleague",
        "The customer or end user"
      ],
      "signalMap": {
        "Just me — I was dealing with it myself": "axis3:self",
        "My team — we were all involved": "axis3:others",
        "A specific colleague": "axis3:others",
        "The customer or end user": "axis3:others"
      },
      "next": "A3_Q2"
    },
    {
      "id": "A3_Q2",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "How did that situation affect others?",
      "options": [
        "It didn’t really affect others",
        "It created some friction for the team",
        "It impacted someone else’s work",
        "It affected the final outcome or user"
      ],
      "signalMap": {
        "It didn’t really affect others": "axis3:self",
        "It created some friction for the team": "axis3:others",
        "It impacted someone else’s work": "axis3:others",
        "It affected the final outcome or user": "axis3:others"
      },
      "next": "A3_DECIDE"
    },
    {
      "id": "A3_DECIDE",
      "type": "decision",
      "conditions": [
        {
          "if": "axis3.others >= axis3.self",
          "goto": "A3_REFLECT_WIDE"
        },
        {
          "if": "axis3.self > axis3.others",
          "goto": "A3_REFLECT_NARROW"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "A3_REFLECT_WIDE",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "You saw how your work connects to others — team, colleagues, even users. That awareness turns effort into impact.",
      "next": "A3_Q3"
    },
    {
      "id": "A3_REFLECT_NARROW",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "It’s natural to experience the day through your own lens. But every action sits inside a larger system — even when it doesn’t feel that way.",
      "next": "A3_Q3"
    },
    {
      "id": "A3_Q3",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "If you looked at today from someone else’s perspective, what might stand out?",
      "options": [
        "They wouldn’t notice much",
        "They’d see the effort I put in",
        "They might have been affected more than I realized",
        "They depended on what I did"
      ],
      "signalMap": {
        "They wouldn’t notice much": "axis3:self",
        "They’d see the effort I put in": "axis3:others",
        "They might have been affected more than I realized": "axis3:others",
        "They depended on what I did": "axis3:others"
      },
      "next": "A3_FINAL"
    },
    {
      "id": "A3_FINAL",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "Work rarely exists in isolation. What you do shapes others — teammates, outcomes, and experiences beyond your immediate view.",
      "next": "SUMMARY"
    },
    {
      "id": "SUMMARY",
      "type": "summary",
      "text": "You approached the day with {axis1.text}.\n\nYou leaned toward {axis2.text}.\n\nYour perspective centered more on {axis3.text}.\n\nA small shift tomorrow can change the entire experience.",
      "next": "END"
    },
    {
      "id": "END",
      "type": "end",
      "text": "That’s it for today. See you tomorrow."
    }
  ]
}